---
import LayoutSidebar from '../../../app/LayoutSidebarClient.astro';
import GelymarLogo from '../../../../public/assets/gelymar.svg';
---

<LayoutSidebar>
  <section class="relative w-full min-h-[80vh] px-6 py-12 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200  dark:from-slate-900 dark:to-slate-800 font-sans animate-fade-in-up pt-28">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Logo -->
      <div class="flex justify-center mb-8">
        <GelymarLogo class="h-24 w-auto" />
      </div>

      <!-- Title -->
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-[#002E50] dark:text-white mb-6 text-center">
        Terms and Conditions
      </h1>

      <!-- Introduction -->
      <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed text-md">
        Welcome to the Gelymar S.A. Management Platform. By accessing or using our platform, you agree to comply with and be bound by the following terms and conditions. Please read them carefully.
      </p>

      <!-- Sections -->
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-2">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">
        By accessing and using this platform, you accept and agree to be bound by the terms and provision of this agreement. If you do not agree to abide by these terms, please do not use this platform.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-2">2. Description of Service</h2>
      <p class="mb-6"> 
        Gelymar S.A. provides a comprehensive management platform designed to support export operations, ensure regulatory compliance, and enhance traceability of products derived from Chilean seaweed.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-2">3. User Responsibilities</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">
        Users are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of their account information and for all activities that occur under their account. Unauthorized use of the platform is strictly prohibited.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-2">4. Data Privacy</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">
        We are committed to protecting your privacy. Our data collection and usage practices are outlined in our <a href="/privacy-policy" class="text-[#00538C] hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a>.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-2">5. Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">
        All content, trademarks, and data on this platform, including but not limited to software, databases, text, graphics, icons, and hyperlinks are the property of or licensed to Gelymar S.A.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-2">6. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">
        Gelymar S.A. shall not be held responsible for any direct, indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from the use or inability to use the platform.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-2">7. Modifications to Terms</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">
        We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Changes will be effective immediately upon posting on the platform. Continued use of the platform constitutes acceptance of the revised terms.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-2">8. Governing Law</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">
        These terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of Chile. Any disputes arising under or in connection with these terms shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts of Santiago, Chile.
      </p>

      <!-- Contact Information -->
      <hr class="my-10 border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600" />
      <p class="text-sm text-center text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
        For any questions or concerns regarding these terms, please contact us at:
        <br />
        📧 <a href="mailto:info@gelymar.com" class="text-[#00538C] hover:underline">info@gelymar.com</a>
        <br />
        📞 +56 2 2989 8000
        <br />
        📍 Av. Pedro de Valdivia Norte 0129, Providencia, Santiago – CHILE
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Animation Styles -->
  <style>
    @keyframes fade-in-up {
      0% { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
      100% { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    .animate-fade-in-up {
      animation: fade-in-up 0.8s ease-out both;
    }
  </style>
</LayoutSidebar>